step.para:
It is recommended that the folder holding the JBoss embedded Media Server files (in this example, the folder named
ms- <version>
) is moved to a user-defined location for storing executable programs. For example, the Program Files folder.

It is recommended that the folder holding the Standalone Media Server files (in this example, the folder named
mms-standalone- <version>
) is moved to a user-defined location for storing executable programs. For example, the Program Files folder.
